Shri T Mohan Dhas is a former senior technical director at National Informatics Centre. He assumed charge as State Informatics Officer at NIC recently. Shri Mohan Dhas has over 30 years of experience in information and communication Technologies and e-Governance in government. Apart from this, he has served in various capacities with eight years at NIC Headquarters in New Delhi, 13 years at NIC Kerala State Centre, seven years at NIC Karnataka State Centre, and last two years as head of NIC Software Development and Training Centre, Kochi.
I welcome you sir, on behalf of our college. I request you to share a few words with us. 
